1.3
log
@use flags instead of options to choose the tea5757 vs tea5759.
from Vladimir Popov <jumbo@@narod.ru>
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: tea5757.h,v 1.2 2001/12/06 16:28:18 mickey Exp $	*/
/* $RuOBSD: tea5757.h,v 1.2 2001/10/18 16:51:36 pva Exp $ */

/*
